{"tid":2499832,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得高達嘅沒落，可以歸咎於劇情太離地","createTime":"2021-04-22T07:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T18:57:33.000Z","uid":105678,"like":3,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"58e92441487224bb5c0b06eaa239083562e1175b","tid":2499832,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUECjuUxwJTYxT3F64KjGFV2bgg9wr2KQQmBDkj9Na7nY?filename=DNmdNtn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNmdNtn.jpg&h=f46dce36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由UC系列開始就好鐘意講啲人世大道理，咩聯邦對自護、人類命運星途。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢啲嘢，對九成人都係冇鳩所謂。<br />\n<br />\n之所以會紅，根本只係因為昭和人經歷過軍國主義有共鳴同渴望和平，同埋會思考未來。<br />\n<br />\n但到平成開始，日本政治黑暗到平民唔想理，呢堆嘢已經變哂離地大道理。<br />\n<br />\n動畫領域，最緊要係時代感。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦vs自護係屬於上一個時代嘅記憶<br />\n<br />\n平成後生仔係比較鍾意情情愛愛，好似seed、鐵血咁，呢啲係屬於我地呢個時代的記憶，成日喺度聽班UC廚說教，乜撚UC屌打新世代。<br />\n<br />\n感覺班人就好似喺度賣弄知識咁，你睇咗咁多年，一定係識多啲架。<br />\n<br />\n樓主我好憎啲UC廚講乜嘢馬反、0096呢啲話題，作為平成後生，根本唔想知道。"},{"pid":"86a845e3038f1af06e02ea75af6cc6007a0d780f","tid":2499832,"uid":229502,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"Seed Destiny無論喺戲內戲外都表達咗戰爭嘅殘酷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNbniekbpWAErv9JeKpLGtgj5GfY8n8NCu9AA1QogR5qw?filename=fwfNRVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwfNRVy.jpg&h=aac115a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ffb7100de28ee11ad3a6c041884d890d66507c5","tid":2499832,"uid":287107,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"86a845e3038f1af06e02ea75af6cc6007a0d780f","tid":2499832,"uid":229502,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:38:12.000Z","msg":"Seed Destiny無論喺戲內戲外都表達咗戰爭嘅殘酷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwfNRVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.